7
00:00:32,800 --> 00:00:33,170
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（过去）</font>

8
00:00:33,170 --> 00:00:33,550
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（曾经）</font>

9
00:00:33,550 --> 00:00:33,920
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（已经结束的事情）</font>

10
00:00:33,920 --> 00:00:34,300
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（或者是——没发生过的事情）</font>

11
00:00:34,300 --> 00:00:34,680
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（连是否曾经存在都无法确定）</font>

12
00:00:34,880 --> 00:00:37,410
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">而小忍之所以能够成为现在的小忍</font>

13
00:00:35,550 --> 00:00:35,800
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（忍）</font>

14
00:00:37,550 --> 00:00:38,550
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（铁血的）</font>

15
00:00:38,550 --> 00:00:39,470
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（热血的）</font>

16
00:00:39,470 --> 00:00:40,470
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（冷血的吸血鬼）</font>

17
00:00:40,470 --> 00:00:41,180
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（抛弃了姬丝秀忒）</font>

18
00:00:40,470 --> 00:00:41,180
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（雅赛劳拉莉昂）</font>

19
00:00:40,470 --> 00:00:41,180
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（刃下心）</font>

20
00:00:40,470 --> 00:00:41,180
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（的名字和姿态）</font>

21
00:00:41,570 --> 00:00:43,320
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">能够以现在小忍的样子陪在我身边</font>

22
00:00:43,820 --> 00:00:47,170
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">说起来  也只是她偶然心血来潮的产物</font>

23
00:00:47,780 --> 00:00:49,440
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">多么令人愉快的心血来潮啊</font>

24
00:00:49,880 --> 00:00:54,540
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">虽然看上去是个幼女  但已经度过了五个多世纪超长人生的她</font>

25
00:00:54,940 --> 00:00:59,320
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">在这些方面说不定出乎意料地很会为我考虑</font>

26
00:00:59,940 --> 00:01:03,900
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">不…不是为我考虑  说到底也只不过是心血来潮罢了</font>

27
00:01:04,700 --> 00:01:10,660
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">这次就来说说她的心血来潮在四百年前究竟起了怎样的作用</font>

28
00:01:11,240 --> 00:01:14,970
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">这是一个讲述在四百年前  她在这个国度有着何等遭遇</font>

29
00:01:15,420 --> 00:01:18,730
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">然后又做了些什么的故事</font>

30
00:01:18,930 --> 00:01:19,180
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（忍野忍）</font>

31
00:01:19,180 --> 00:01:19,430
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（这是一个回溯她的时间线的故事）</font>

32
00:01:19,430 --> 00:01:19,930
