33
00:01:30,230 --> 00:01:32,330
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">而我  阿良良木历也是如此</font>

34
00:01:30,230 --> 00:01:30,560
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（我）</font>

35
00:01:32,770 --> 00:01:34,530
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">就让我边回忆着「她」边向你们讲述吧</font>

