<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">不过我现在联系不上她</font>

408
00:16:20,780 --> 00:16:21,200
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（忍野的老熟人)</font>

409
00:16:21,500 --> 00:16:22,120
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">顺带一问</font>

410
00:16:22,120 --> 00:16:24,770
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">影缝小姐现在在哪里做些什么呢</font>

411
00:16:25,250 --> 00:16:26,990
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">我想她大概也在忙工作吧</font>

412
00:16:27,320 --> 00:16:29,080
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">虽说她确实是在工作</font>

413
00:16:29,220 --> 00:16:31,490
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">不过细节肯定是要保密的啊</font>

414
00:16:31,930 --> 00:16:34,530
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">你在打听什么内部情报啊  真是厚脸皮</font>

415
00:16:34,800 --> 00:16:37,730
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">我倒不是厚着脸皮来问你的…</font>

416
00:16:37,500 --> 00:16:37,840
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（只不过是客套话而已）</font>

417
00:16:37,840 --> 00:16:38,170
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（阴阳师界的保密义务）</font>

418
00:16:38,170 --> 00:16:38,510
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（比想象中的还要严格啊）</font>

419
00:16:38,770 --> 00:16:42,540
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">算了  就算联系不上影缝小姐也没什么问题</font>

420
00:16:43,020 --> 00:16:45,510
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">反正一到晚上就会真相大白了</font>

421
00:16:45,850 --> 00:16:47,340
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">嗯？为什么？</font>

422
00:16:47,690 --> 00:16:52,020
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">难道说一到晚上鬼哥哥就会突然变聪明吗</font>

423
00:16:52,330 --> 00:16:54,420
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">我可没有那么方便的功能</font>

424
00:16:55,080 --> 00:16:56,980
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">只是小忍会醒过来罢了</font>

425
00:16:59,890 --> 00:17:02,370
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">别看小忍那个样子  她可是怪异之王</font>

426
00:17:02,740 --> 00:17:04,520
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">对于怪异的事情她应该很清楚才对</font>

427
00:17:04,730 --> 00:17:08,970
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">而且她还在和影缝小姐同为怪异专家的忍野咩咩那里</font>

428
00:17:09,160 --> 00:17:12,200
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">接受了长达数个月的精英教育</font>

429
00:17:12,760 --> 00:17:16,880
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">她一定掌握着与那个黑暗有关的知识</font>

430
00:17:17,340 --> 00:17:21,170
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">所以只要小忍一醒过来  就能知道那个黑暗的真面目了</font>

431
00:17:21,560 --> 00:17:23,680
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">哼  根本信不过啊</font>

432
00:17:23,880 --> 00:17:25,890
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">那种晚期高龄者的知识</font>

433
00:17:26,220 --> 00:17:28,890
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">别再把小忍叫做晚期高龄者了</font>

434
00:17:29,480 --> 00:17:32,960
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">确实小忍也不一定就知道那个黑暗是什么</font>

435
00:17:33,460 --> 00:17:34,880
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">但是斧乃木妹妹</font>

436
00:17:35,200 --> 00:17:36,770
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">那其实也无所谓</font>

437
00:17:37,460 --> 00:17:38,180
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">为什么</font>

438
00:17:38,540 --> 00:17:41,090
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">因为小忍会吃掉怪异</font>

439
00:17:42,090 --> 00:17:44,520
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">无论那个不明物体的真面目是什么</font>

440
00:17:44,800 --> 00:17:45,970
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">她都会把它整个吞下去的</font>

441
00:17:46,640 --> 00:17:48,160
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">而那个黑暗之谜</font>

442
00:17:48,440 --> 00:17:50,570
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">只要过几天去问问羽川就行了</font>

443
00:17:51,050 --> 00:17:52,790
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">羽川？那是谁？</font>

444
00:17:53,480 --> 00:17:54,840
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">一个什么都知道的家伙</font>

445
00:17:57,210 --> 00:18:01,760
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">不过我觉得像你这样把麻烦全都推给别人还是有点问题</font>

446
00:18:02,380 --> 00:18:06,280
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">虽然这话从不知不觉就救了鬼哥哥的我嘴里说出来也有些奇怪</font>

447
00:18:07,780 --> 00:18:08,760
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">那就再见了</font>

448
00:18:09,170 --> 00:18:10,080
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">再见？</font>

449
00:18:10,400 --> 00:18:11,980
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">怎么  你要回去了吗</font>

450
00:18:12,420 --> 00:18:14,980
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">与其说是回去  不如说是回去工作</font>

451
00:18:15,370 --> 00:18:18,860
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">你难道不是要跟着我保护我一辈子吗</font>

452
00:18:19,260 --> 00:18:20,360
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">你到底是怎么想的</font>

453
00:18:20,700 --> 00:18:21,600
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">我是在开玩笑</font>

454
00:18:21,890 --> 00:18:23,810
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">至少你已经保护过我一次了</font>

455
00:18:24,120 --> 00:18:26,360
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">说起来我还没有向你道谢呢</font>

456
00:18:26,620 --> 00:18:27,340
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">谢谢</font>

457
00:18:27,690 --> 00:18:29,780
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">我今后一定会报答你的</font>

458
00:18:30,020 --> 00:18:30,740
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">用肌肉来报答吗</font>

459
00:18:31,100 --> 00:18:33,240
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">不  用肌肉之外的某种东西…</font>

460
00:18:33,240 --> 00:18:33,620
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（如果你非要不可的话）</font>

461
00:18:33,620 --> 00:18:34,120
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（我倒也不是不能…）</font>

462
00:18:34,120 --> 00:18:34,500
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（挖一块肌肉出来给你…）</font>

463
00:18:34,980 --> 00:18:37,360
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">因为我不知道什么时候就会从这个世界上消失</font>

464
00:18:37,530 --> 00:18:39,410
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">所以站在我的立场上来说</font>

465
00:18:39,850 --> 00:18:42,500
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">恩情之类的必须当场还清</font>

466
00:18:42,500 --> 00:18:44,010
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（当场）</font>

467
00:18:42,820 --> 00:18:43,920
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">当场还清…</font>

468
00:18:44,490 --> 00:18:47,130
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">那有没有什么我现在就能做到的事情呢</font>

469
00:18:47,650 --> 00:18:50,140
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">鬼哥哥现在就能做到的事情啊…</font>

470
00:18:50,650 --> 00:18:52,390
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">嗯  让我想想…</font>

471
00:18:52,770 --> 00:18:56,130
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">虽然我能做到的事情不多</font>

472
00:18:56,520 --> 00:18:57,720
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">但还请你尽情吩咐</font>

473
00:18:57,810 --> 00:18:58,520
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">哪怕只是说说看也好</font>

474
00:19:01,440 --> 00:19:02,400
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">鬼哥哥</font>

475
00:19:02,820 --> 00:19:03,330
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">啊？</font>

476
00:19:04,280 --> 00:19:05,070
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">脸转到这边来</font>

477
00:19:05,720 --> 00:19:06,070
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">亲</font>

478
00:19:06,070 --> 00:19:06,440
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（被夺走了）</font>

479
00:19:06,440 --> 00:19:06,860
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（突然之间）</font>

480
00:19:10,730 --> 00:19:12,240
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">纳…纳尼怒捏诺</font>

481
00:19:12,620 --> 00:19:13,680
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">啦哩噜咧咯</font>

482
00:19:15,580 --> 00:19:17,480
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">啊啊  你花心</font>

483
00:19:17,680 --> 00:19:20,040
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">鬼哥哥真是个见异思迁的男人</font>

484
00:19:21,040 --> 00:19:21,420
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（这孩子究竟在说些什么！？）</font>

485
00:19:21,420 --> 00:19:21,920
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（面无表情地说些什么呢！？）</font>

486
00:19:22,220 --> 00:19:28,850
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">我只不过是想告诉你所谓信赖关系是很容易就会被破坏的</font>

487
00:19:29,610 --> 00:19:31,800
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">与其说是你回报了我的恩情</font>

488
00:19:31,890 --> 00:19:34,060
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">不如说是你欠我的恩情又增加了</font>

489
00:19:34,480 --> 00:19:36,760
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">你穿的还真多啊  鬼哥哥</font>

490
00:19:37,000 --> 00:19:38,940
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">不过我也一下子爽快了不少</font>

491
00:19:40,440 --> 00:19:41,060
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（这是在）</font>

492
00:19:41,060 --> 00:19:41,690
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（晒给）</font>

493
00:19:41,690 --> 00:19:42,690
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（小忍看吗）</font>

494
00:19:43,130 --> 00:19:43,500
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">再见</font>

495
00:19:43,980 --> 00:19:45,690
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">努力活下去吧</font>

496
00:19:46,140 --> 00:19:47,820
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">在这个规则不明的游戏中</font>

497
00:19:48,450 --> 00:19:50,360
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">这才不是什么游戏呢</font>

498
00:19:50,890 --> 00:19:51,720
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">那是什么？</font>

499
00:19:55,150 --> 00:20:02,260
<font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}今もずっとその声を覚えてるから</font>

500
00:19:55,150 --> 00:20:02,260
<font face="STZhongsong" size="39" color="#f6d440">现在我也记得你的声音</font>

501
00:20:11,750 --> 00:20:14,360
<font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}あの日走った道に</font>

502
00:20:11,750 --> 00:20:14,360
<font face="STZhongsong" size="39" color="#f6d440">那些日子走过的路</font>

503
00:20:14,560 --> 00:20:17,180
<font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}あの日見上げた空に</font>

504
00:20:14,560 --> 00:20:17,180
<font face="STZhongsong" size="39" color="#f6d440">那些日子仰望的天空</font>

505
00:20:17,420 --> 00:20:22,430
<font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}二度と返らない時を重ねてる</font>

506
00:20:17,420 --> 00:20:22,430
<font face="STZhongsong" size="39" color="#f6d440">无法回去的曾经反复叠加</font>

507
00:20:22,990 --> 00:20:25,630
<font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}君は笑うだろうか</font>

508
00:20:22,990 --> 00:20:25,630
<font face="STZhongsong" size="39" color="#f6d440">你恐怕会笑我吧</font>

509
00:20:25,760 --> 00:20:28,420
<font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}少し怒るだろうね</font>

510
00:20:25,760 --> 00:20:28,420
<font face="STZhongsong" size="39" color="#f6d440">会有一丝生气吧</font>

511
00:20:28,640 --> 00:20:34,150
<font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}こんな諦め悪い僕のことを</font>

512
00:20:28,640 --> 00:20:34,150
<font face="STZhongsong" size="39" color="#f6d440">我就是这么一个无法死心的人</font>

513
00:20:34,800 --> 00:20:37,840
<font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}何度でも</font>

514
00:20:34,800 --> 00:20:37,840
<font face="STZhongsong" size="39" color="#f6d440">一次又一次</font>

515
00:20:38,150 --> 00:20:43,790
<font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}迂闊に願う可能性を清書して  （いつまでも）</font>

516
00:20:38,150 --> 00:20:43,790
<font face="STZhongsong" size="39" color="#f6d440">将那些恍惚间许愿的可能性整理起来  （直到永远）</font>

517
00:20:43,780 --> 00:20:48,350
<font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}まだ迷いそうに騙されてたくて</font>

518
00:20:43,780 --> 00:20:48,350
<font face="STZhongsong" size="39" color="#f6d440">都想这样迷茫地被自己所欺骗</font>

519
00:20:48,790 --> 00:20:53,910
<font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}だから「どうかせめて」なんて思う心は</font>

520
00:20:48,790 --> 00:20:53,910
<font face="STZhongsong" size="39" color="#f6d440">因此许下这些愿望的心情</font>

521
00:20:54,040 --> 00:20:57,400
<font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}一時的な感傷だって</font>

522
00:20:54,040 --> 00:20:57,400
<font face="STZhongsong" size="39" color="#f6d440">这些暂时的感伤</font>

523
00:20:57,600 --> 00:20:59,870
<font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}許せばいい</font>

524
00:20:57,600 --> 00:20:59,870
<font face="STZhongsong" size="39" color="#f6d440">只要认可就好</font>

525
00:21:00,060 --> 00:21:02,910
<font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}だからそうさ君がやっと</font>

526
00:21:00,060 --> 00:21:02,910
<font face="STZhongsong" size="39" color="#f6d440">因此请让我对你说</font>

527
00:21:03,040 --> 00:21:05,190
<font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}絶望の先で</font>

528
00:21:03,040 --> 00:21:05,190
<font face="STZhongsong" size="39" color="#f6d440">在我绝望的时候</font>

529
00:21:05,380 --> 00:21:14,380
<font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}くれた日々に偽りなんてないと言ってあげよう</font>

530
00:21:05,380 --> 00:21:14,380
<font face="STZhongsong" size="39" color="#f6d440">你曾给我带来的那些日子没有虚假</font>

531
00:21:16,070 --> 00:21:20,360
<font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}忘れないで</font>

532
00:21:16,070 --> 00:21:20,360
<font face="STZhongsong" size="39" color="#f6d440">不要将我忘记</font>

533
00:21:28,940 --> 00:21:32,370
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">对于斧乃木妹妹离开了之后所产生的进一步状况</font>

534
00:21:32,540 --> 00:21:33,090
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">我不寒而栗</font>

535
00:21:36,530 --> 00:21:37,850
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">八九寺睡着了</font>

536
00:21:38,400 --> 00:21:40,010
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">那也就是说不管做什么都可以吧</font>

537
00:21:41,140 --> 00:21:43,840
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">吸血鬼铁拳！</font>

538
00:21:49,250 --> 00:21:52,450
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">哈  真是千钧一发啊</font>

539
00:21:52,970 --> 00:21:54,990
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">看来吾醒来的真是时候</font>

540
00:21:55,740 --> 00:21:55,990
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（真是时候）</font>

541
00:21:57,400 --> 00:22:00,330
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">你实际上不才睡了两个小时吗</font>

542
00:22:00,680 --> 00:22:04,260
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">刚才吾睡得特别浅  完全没法睡着</font>

543
00:22:04,740 --> 00:22:06,840
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">疲劳一点都没消除</font>

544
00:22:07,250 --> 00:22:08,420
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">到底发生什么事了</font>

545
